  "description": "Product Description Vaseline Lip Therapy Original 20g Vaseline Lip Therapy Original has been known for years as a well-known product in the field of lip care. Thanks to salve your dry lips are restored and they do not dry out. This is especially great in the hot summer months and in extreme cold. No more dry or chapped lips thanks to Vaseline Lip Therapy Original! Contents: 20 gr Ingredients Petrolatum Directions 1. Apply Vaseline Lip Therapy Original directly to dry or chapped lips as needed. 2. Use before bedtime for best results. 3. Protect lips from harsh weather conditions by applying before going outside in cold or hot weather. 4. For external use only. Safety Warning As we are always looking to improve our products, our formulations change from time to time, so please always check the product packaging before use Manufacturer Contact Information Unilever Dept ER, Wirral, CH63 3JW, UK. See more",
